data.description: PACK YOUR BAGS! This one is clean as a whistle and move-in ready! Charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom with an open, bright design and a soft tan palette that will blend with any design style. With stainless steel appliances adorning the modern kitchen, meal prep becomes a joy. Spacious, fenced-in backyard with open patio perfect for hosting a neighborhood barbecue or just relaxing outside in the autumn sun, enjoy evenings outside with your fire pit. Experience the convenience of shopping, dining, and entertainment options just minutes away. This is more than a house; it's a place where memories are made. Schedule a viewing today and step into your future!
